result.title: 1990 - 1990 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Southern North Sea and English Channel Plankton Survey - RV Corystes 01/90
result.name: 1990-1990-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-southern-north-sea-a-01-90
result.notes:
Analysis of plankton samples collected as part of the International Council 
for the Exploration of the Sea (ICES) coordinated herring larvae survey of 
ICES Regions IVc and VIId (Southern North Sea and Eastern English Channel). 
Plankton samples were collected at each site on a planned survey grid. Dataset 
consists of the numbers and lengths of herring, sprat and pilchard larvae, 
along with associated positional data and volumes filtered.
